# A [[unit]] of the police specifically trained to deal with [[riot#Verb|riot]]ing crowds. They use special equipment for personal defense as well as for [[crowd]] control and [[dispersal]].

====Usage notes====
* As a collective noun, the riot police are referred to using plural pronouns and verb forms, such as ''they'' and ''were''.

